        <bioghist id="ref9">
            <head>Biographical/Historical Note</head>
            <p>American Trotskyist and subsequently socialist; Fourth International representative, Mexico, 1938-1939.</p>
        </bioghist>
        <scopecontent id="ref10">
            <head>Scope and Content of Collection</head>
            <p>Correspondence, writings, notes, minutes, reports, resolutions, and printed matter, relating to internal divisions within the Mexican section of the Fourth International, Fourth International activities elsewhere, relations between Leon Trotsky and Diego Rivera, and theoretical debates in Trotskyist and social democratic circles.</p>
